---

<div data-eval-component="FeatureGridEven" class="community-section"><div class="w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="collection-item-18 w-dyn-item"><div class="wrapper community"><div class="community-image-container"><img loading="lazy" alt="Beta Gym" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63caaac34d6a3583a0074c0d/63ce2c0a8a1d4b999b2ecde2_Community%20at%20Beta%20Gym%20Modern%20in%20Manhattan.jpg" class="community-image"><div class="about-us-section-image-border"></div></div><div class="about-us-section-text-container"><div class="heading-wrapper community"><h2 class="heading-11"><strong>{communityHeadline ?? "A Community That Will Keep You Going"}</strong></h2></div><div class="paragraph-wrapper"><div class="w-richtext"><p>Joining a gym shouldn't be intimidating. We will help you feel comfortable getting started.<br><br>Beta Gym has been around for years helping people reach their fitness goals.<br><br>We are striving to help every person find a higher quality of life through greater health.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>

